Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques such as Long-Short Term Memory networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of feature engineering and optimization, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
